ia]] {{flagicon|ESP}}\n|score      = 2\u20130\n|aet        = yes\n|report     = [http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2003/matches/round=1721/match=74499/index.html Report]\n|team2      = {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K.|Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi]]\n|goals1     = [[Mista (footballer)|Mista]] {{goal|63}}<br>[[Vicente Rodr\u00edguez|Vicente]] {{goal|94}}\n|stadium    = [[Mestalla Stadium]], [[Valencia]]\n|attendance = \n|referee    = [[Ren\u00e9 Temmink]] ([[Royal Dutch Football Association|Netherlands]])\n}}\n''Valencia won 2\u20131 on aggregate.''\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=notes}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K.}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2003-04 Genclerbirligi S.K. season}}\n[[Category:Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K. seasons]]\n[[Category:Turkish football clubs 2003\u201304 season|Genclerbirligi S.K.]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Football club season\n| club             = [[Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K.]]\n| season           = 2003\u201304\n| chairman         = \n| manager          = {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Ersun Yanal]]\n| league           = [[S\u00fcper Lig]]\n| league result    = [[2003\u201304 S\u00fcper Lig|10th]]\n| league topscorer = [[Souleymane Youla]] (16)\n| season topscorer = \n| cup1             = [[Turkish Cup]]\n| cup1 result      = [[2003\u201304 Turkish Cup|Runners-up]]\n| cup2             = [[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]]\n| cup2 result      = [[2003\u201304 UEFA Cup#Fourth round|Fourth round]]\n| prevseason       = [[2002\u201303 Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K. season|2002\u201303]]\n| nextseason       = [[2004\u201305 Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K. season|2004\u201305]]\n}}\nDuring the '''2003\u201304''' Turkish football season, Gen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi S.K. competed in the S\u00fcper Lig.\n\n==Season summary==\nGen\u00e7lerbirli\u011fi reached the fourth round of the UEFA Cup before being knocked out by eventual runners-up Valencia.\n\n==First-team squad==\n:''Squad at end of season''\n{{fs start}}\n{{Fs p